item.title: And who’s gonna end up holdin’ your hand-
item.description: And who’s gonna end up holdin’ your hand- A beautiful woman or a tall, handsome man? There’s no doubt they’ll love you, but it’s yet to be seen: Will anyone ever know you like me? Will anyone ever know you like me? “Like Me” – Chely Wright
